鎖.definition: to lock; to lock up; a lock (CL:把[ba3])

鎖吶.definition: suona, Chinese shawm; see 嗩吶|唢呐

鎖國.definition: to close a country; to exclude foreign contact; closed country (Qing China, North Korea etc)

鎖定.definition: to lock (a door); to close with a latch; to lock into place; a lock; a latch; to lock a computer file (to prevent it being overwritten); to lock (denying access to a computer system or device or files, e.g. by password-protection); to focus attention on; to target

鎖屏.definition: (computing) to lock the screen; lock screen

鎖掉.definition: lock up; lock out; to lock

鎖閂.definition: latch; bolt (to lock a door or window)
